posting_body: ['b>', 'California Oaks | Call or Text', 'show contact info', '2 Bedroom, 1 Bath', 'Sq Ft:906 Aprox.', 'Rent: $ 2895.00', 'Deposit: $1000.00', 'California Oaks is a carefully maintained garden-style apartment community conveniently located in Mountain View, home to Google and many other internet titans.', 'Mountain View is a very special city offering great dining, access to parks and is close to the ease of public transportation such as Caltrain.', 'If you like hiking and biking both are available in your backyard on numerous access trails.', 'We offer spacious 1 and 2 bedroom apartments that boast maple cabinets throughout.', 'Please call us today to schedule a tour!', 'Features', '•\tLarge Closets', '•\tEfficient Appliances', '•\tSkylight', '•\tRefrigerator', '•\tMicrowave', '•\tWindow Coverings', '•\tExtra Storage', '•\tDishwasher', '•\tCable Ready', '•\tWood', '•\tCarpeting', '•\tDisposal', 'Community Amenities', '•\tRecycling', '•\tLaundry Facilities', '•\tCourtyard', '•\tBBQ/ Picnic Area', '•\tClubhouse', '•\tCovered Parking', 'Office Hours', 'Tuesday-Saturday 9:00AM-6:00pm', 'Pet Policy', 'Not a pet friendly community.', 'Income Requirements:', 'Gross monthly income must be 2.75 times the monthly rent.', 'Lease Term:', '6, 9, and 12 month lease, utilities residents responsible, renters insurance required.', 'Equal Housing Opportunity', 'Professionally managed by Prodesse Property Group Find additional properties with in our company on <URL>.']
